{
  "stem": "7781.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no such a thing like-- you know, you took chances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What the hell?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, to get out, you-- you say anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You would say people lie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We just want to save ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went there, and he figured-- he asked, what are you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told him I'm a klempner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Klempner is a sheet metal worker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we registered-- registered all four-- all four of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- and they took us out, but nine days later, they asked us to report to a certain place, and they took us out of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And where did you go to?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We took-- went to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-- B-R-O-N-S-H-W-E-I-G.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got to Braunschweig, and from there, we stayed in one camp, a small camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us to Vechelde.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "W-O-C-H-E-L-D-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Vechelde was a factory, a metal-working, a-- They were building parts for trucks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there they're-- we're assigned to a German worker we called a [? masters, ?] you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would show you what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- me and my brother were assigned to a guy, to a German, and we had a big drill press, and we're supposed to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He showed us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I was no-- we learned fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was an automatic machine, and we learned fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the process, I almost lost three fingers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there we stayed, in this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not-- in the beginning, we were physically abused by the kapo-- by the [GERMAN] They were the German criminals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the worst enemy there was the cold and the hunger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no defense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was a constant hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'd get that little piece of bread, and the soup, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
